Hollywood praises actors who transform their bodies for roles—but behind the praise is a much darker reality. From extreme weight loss to dangerous bulking, these transformations often push actors to the brink, both physically and mentally. In this video, we dive into the hidden pain, pressure, and consequences behind some of the most extreme body changes in film history.
